# Sofia Hotel Receptionist - Implementation Guide

## 📁 File Structure

```
agents/hotel/
├── sofia_hotel_receptionist.py  ✅ PRODUCTION (Pure Console - Use This!)
├── sofia_hotel_web.py           🌐 WEB INTERFACE (Browser/Testing)
└── hotel_agent.py                📦 ORIGINAL (Backup/Reference)
```

## 🎯 Which Version to Use?

### ✅ **sofia_hotel_receptionist.py** (RECOMMENDED)
**Use for: Hotel front desk production deployment**

```bash
/Users/tolga/Desktop/elvi/sofia-pers/local-voice-ai-agent/.venv/bin/python sofia_hotel_receptionist.py receptionist
```

**Features:**
- ✅ Pure console mode - No browser needed
- ✅ Direct microphone/speaker interaction
- ✅ Perfect for kiosk/reception desk
- ✅ Listens for 5 seconds, processes, responds
- ✅ Say "goodbye" to end session
- ✅ Clean terminal output

**Perfect for:**
- Hotel reception desk
- Guest service kiosk
- Front desk assistant
- Self-service check-in

